         <div type="translation" resp="part:argr part:vito">
             <p>Success! In the year <gap reason="lost"/> of <persName type="human" subtype="coronation"><roleName type="king">King Vāsiṭṭhīputta Sāmisiripuḷumāvi</roleName></persName> <gap reason="lost"/> a Dharma-wheel has been established at <placeName type="builtPlace" subtype="temple">the Great Shrine</placeName> <supplied reason="lost">of the Bhagavant</supplied>, at <supplied reason="subaudible">its</supplied> western gate, in the possession of the order of the Cetikiyas as pious gift of the notable <persName type="human"><roleName type="unknown" subtype="donor">Kahutara</roleName></persName> of the Piṇḍasutariyas and of <persName type="human">Isila</persName>, son of the notable <persName type="human">Puri</persName>, with his brother<supplied reason="subaudible">s</supplied>, his sister<supplied reason="subaudible">s</supplied>, and together with his wife <persName type="human">Nākānikā</persName>, and with his son<supplied reason="subaudible">s</supplied> <gap reason="lost"/></p>
